    • Field Detail

      • REST_URI_DEFAULT

        public static final String REST_URI_DEFAULT
        This variable defines the REST URI used in OpenInfRA. It contains the schema definition (projects or system) and the UUID of the project as regular expression. The slash and the project UUID are optional and are not used for the system schema.

      • REST_URI_PRIMER

        public static final String REST_URI_PRIMER
        This variable defines the REST URI for primer requests. It contains the schema definition (system, rbac or metadata). The schema projects is not supported. For the schema projects use REST_URI_PROJECTS instead.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • UTF8_CHARSET

        public static final String UTF8_CHARSET
        This variable defines the character set utf8 which is returned by the REST services. This definition has been chosen in order to avoid wrong character sets while using JSP templates. JSP templates define its own contentType and pageEncoding. The usage of this variable overrides the character set defined by a JSP template.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • HTML_PRIORITY

        public static final String HTML_PRIORITY
        This variable defines the priority of HTML response. Used for older browsers which don't provide its own priority setting.
